Description:
vsnzprintf() function: print formatted output from an stdarg argument list
to a fixed length string (without INT_MAX limitation)

Files:
lib/vsnzprintf.c

Depends-on:
stdio-h
vasnprintf
errno-h
stdint-h

configure.ac:
gl_STDIO_MODULE_INDICATOR([vsnzprintf])

Makefile.am:
lib_SOURCES += vsnzprintf.c

Include:
<stdio.h>

